bugzilla #843013

reorder bits, to start with node id and then time in natural order

this distributes data from different nodes into different buckets, but keeps
data from the same batches close to each other increasing data locality
improves bulk indexing to a local sqlite on an SSD by about 15% - likely more
on non-ssd mysql (will validate that)
